      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 36,
      "message": "From my point of view, this class is doing too much. It is both an entity with properties, but also contains all the sending logic.\nAt some point in time we should refactor this to better separate these concerns.\nI think doing that in this CR would be too much, but it would also help performance I guess because it saves the reinitialization of the service related logic for each entity",
